{"tid":2097863,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[三思] 講過唔放棄任何一條有機會贏嘅戰綫嘅你，點解會萌生咗7.11、7.12唔去投票嘅念頭？","createTime":"2020-07-07T05:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T10:42:47.000Z","uid":258706,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"75d39753a44c860c691f90893136bdf5462402a6","tid":2097863,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"由11月區選開始就決定<span style=\"color: orange;\">有票必投、寸土必爭、唔放棄任一條贏嘅戰綫</span>嘅你，點解喺6月之後，就再唔想諗立法會戰綫點贏嘅？<br />\n<br />\n係咪因為<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法生效咗，你覺得喺議會入面點抗爭都無用、爭取唔到五大訴求被落實呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你咁諗，你已經墜入咗<span style=\"color: violet;\">共產黨嘅圈套</span>，共產黨至所以喺呢個時間實施國安法，係想<span style=\"color: violet;\">將選舉氣氛降温</span>同<span style=\"color: violet;\">等你覺得立法會過半冇用</span><br />\n<br />\n的而且確，國安法係恐嚇緊想透過拉布/否決財政預算案以迫使政府落實五大訴求嘅參選人，令佢哋被DQ，搞到好多人<span style=\"color: teal;\">覺得香港冇喇、35+過到都冇機會實現到五大訴求</span>同去<span style=\"color: teal;\">放棄立法會選舉戰綫</span><br />\n<br />\n係，五大訴求喺呢刻真係<span style=\"color: gold;\">好難透過立法會戰綫被落實</span>，但35+真係成功嘅話，我哋可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔駛再拉布，直接否決唔係&ldquo;香港人優先&rdquo;嘅議案</span>，從而<span style=\"color: gold;\">阻止香港赤化</span>，eg否決大大小小&ldquo;中國人優先&rdquo;嘅議案同撥款，35+齊心嘅話，喺唔駛拉布嘅情況下所有新嘅親中社團大樓、跨境通道、口岸全部都起唔到，大陸人優先、優惠待遇嘅政策隨即被否決<br />\n<br />\n有啲人可能會話，<span style=\"color: brown;\">咁諗會唔會太天真吖？</span>你覺得過半之後，政府唔會DQ我哋陣營嘅人？冇用喇、冇用喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我真係屌曬啲咁諗嘅人吖！</span></span>之前又話唔放棄任何戰綫，依家話有風險就唔做，咁乜戰綫都有風險咖啦，依家用合法嘅方式去做，落街投個票你都唔肯？非親中派喺特區議會未試過過半數，唔試又點知唔得，唔過半又點阻止到香港赤化？政府DQ人係佢嘅問題，至少我哋做好咗自己、後悔先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家嘅狀況似2015、2016年，政府喺傘運失敗之後大潑無力感，等我哋做返港豬，不理世事、唔去抗爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果我哋唔三思，揀放棄立會戰綫，到頭來只會重蹈2016年光復立法會失敗嘅覆轍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，你諗吓<span style=\"color: brown;\">已犧牲自己嘅手足</span>，你覺得佢哋會想我哋贏定輸，想見到我哋盡咗力但失敗定乜都唔理等直接失敗，<span style=\"color: brown;\">我哋冇出過力打呢條戰綫，真係對得住佢哋咩</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人仲話肺炎再爆發，落街投票不了<br />\n香港人因為怕肺炎喺二月開始縮，取消咗唔少集會同遊行，結果三月就換嚟政府打壓、以疫限聚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我哋再因為少少零聲個案而縮，<span style=\"color: blue;\">打壓必然進一步咁嚟</span>，到時連渣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就算35+實現唔到五大訴求，都要阻止香港進一步赤化</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.11/ 7.12 票站見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"bc92607bf029a5a3b16bfda4cd4f0ce9f5e54b90","tid":2097863,"uid":310970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:53:12.000Z","msg":"投票都驚？ 我就一定投"},{"pid":"d68fbb92d631112f9631d4e4842af30cd4ad176f","tid":2097863,"uid":20558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"7.11-12 投票師召喚"},{"pid":"2b749be3f0a750ec7354f32d52e1470e7dc9f0ca","tid":2097863,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"61ca33e31f2537079b945cf65b12e4fe4889af20","tid":2097863,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:02:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77b012c82c9fa50822fd303dd6663e1fd85d83c4","tid":2097863,"uid":340040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"7.11/ 7.12 票站見<br />\n個人覺得35+已經唔係唯一目標，初選係選民意代表同做國際線"},{"pid":"4fe1fa5111d484fbdfc4573c2991e59dbb0aa352","tid":2097863,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76957429d7b8cceb0919d0dd81d2ddb0278e1089","tid":2097863,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77b012c82c9fa50822fd303dd6663e1fd85d83c4","tid":2097863,"uid":340040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"7.11/ 7.12 票站見<br />\n個人覺得35+已經唔係唯一目標，初選係選民意代表同做國際線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"國際會睇我哋嘅選舉結果而去決定幫我哋幾多  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 711/712票站要人吖"},{"pid":"37ce7c124406b04a2e2203b0826eb267edcfe1c3","tid":2097863,"uid":348352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5cd1ef814c36fd80f0d48341bde644709f5d4f","tid":2097863,"uid":340040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76957429d7b8cceb0919d0dd81d2ddb0278e1089","tid":2097863,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77b012c82c9fa50822fd303dd6663e1fd85d83c4","tid":2097863,"uid":340040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"7.11/ 7.12 票站見<br />\n個人覺得35+已經唔係唯一目標，初選係選民意代表同做國際線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"國際會睇我哋嘅選舉結果而去決定幫我哋幾多  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 711/712票站要人吖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"表現反抗意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b569776e4775121874075f6dacb15df18698bbb","tid":2097863,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"票站見，吾咁話有咩用，但冇理由投張票都吾做。"},{"pid":"d6e9431b34b0ceecceee3a16afb7b4f59890e0a7","tid":2097863,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JApxhcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJApxhcd.png&h=4862bc64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57b13d94e610efb635f411a90570aa095c4e2cd0","tid":2097863,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"914dc4240511fc4accee38b5bfb33022c2a97a