33975","tid":2097863,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n711 712 票站見"},{"pid":"1f2f1a0dd52f0d3e8a3f1d86ca0fd59d56f155c4","tid":2097863,"uid":3086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"記得有本土投本土 超區推王百羽上去<br />\n<br />\n當年好多人都講「我想投6號梁天琦架，不過今次投左關鍵一席楊岳橋先」現實係以後無得再投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次初選，就用選票將我地嘅聲音推俾全香港聽，好嗎？"},{"pid":"b45229371706c92c537b1e6358051f581ff40c92","tid":2097863,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄任何戰線"},{"pid":"6dfaa4dbc93841f4e65771a9f449a002938bc151","tid":2097863,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13ef355a558a07035cfa697aef7b3db2b6fcaafc","tid":2097863,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c53c42de3298363bc6e9898be17f1781e665a96","tid":2097863,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:50:18.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔知今個星期就投票<br />\n我諗出面大把人唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4671dbc504898abfdc61113567d5bfc938653c3","tid":2097863,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n投票當遊行<br />\n表達大家反抗嘅民意<br />\n希望當日見到奇跡"},{"pid":"27e6bcc9d924e09f8f20aed50ccad519417b81d1","tid":2097863,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c53c42de3298363bc6e9898be17f1781e665a96","tid":2097863,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2